ssets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585d394f9c8491dc538e5c7969093b5c43b41011","tid":1392703,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8d3aa9ff293c393ae402db0e9130c46500254f","tid":1392703,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:49:13.000Z","msg":"我哋由612開始爭取成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n不過，我哋從來冇討論過委員會由咩人去組成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人分析琴日中共為成立獨立調查委員會開綠燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋係時候開始討論當中嘅細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n試過有法官判示威者以胸部襲警後，相信大家都明白香港有好多紅底法官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以獨立調查委員會一定唔可以只係有本地法官組成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要嘅獨立調查委員會係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>由國際專家、聯合國，甚至海牙軍事法庭嘅人組成</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>拒絕港共自己人查自己人<br />\n<br />\n要由國際專家調查事件</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300d026a2ac354f33e0dae20d6df84ff1143c099","tid":1392703,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"692d81c21950a3ae85e99cfb64dafde4a1dcfc48","tid":1